Sentence:
GGO developed after the lung cancer diagnosis, deteriorated after the initiation of osimertinib, 
and incompletely decreased after interrupting osimertinib;
therefore, flexible bronchoscopy was performed.

The expression levels of PADI4 and GBP1 varied with smoking history and histopathological type,
 while miR-215 and TMB were associated with multiple clinical characteristics,
 including age and TNM stage.
